document.title: Online shopping
title: Online shopping
subtitle: Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered goods or services online within the last year
longtitle0_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered clothes (including sport clothing), shoes or accessories online within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle0_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
longtitle1_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered sports goods (excluding sport clothing) online within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle1_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
longtitle2_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered consumer electronics or household appliances online within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle2_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
longtitle3_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered films or series as a streaming service or downloads online within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle3_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
longtitle4_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who booked tickets to cultural or other events within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle4_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
longtitle5_0: (Share of women/men aged 16 to 74 who ordered rented accommodation from an enterprises or a private person online within the last three months prior to the survey,
longtitle5_1: in % of all woman/men the same age who used the internet within the last year)
